sequenceDiagram
    participant G as 5.x gRPC Client
    participant A as GrpcMessagingApplication
    participant D as DefaultGrpcMessagingActivity
    participant S as SendMessageActivity
    participant M as MessagingProcessor
    participant B as Broker SendMessageProcessor

    G->>A: SendMessage RPC
    A->>D: sendMessage()
    D->>S: sendMessage()
    S->>S: 校验并转换 Message
    S->>M: sendMessage(...)
    M->>B: 本地调用或 Remoting 转发
    B-->>G: SendMessageResponse
